description:
BRAND NEW 
IN HAND READY TO SHIP

The Nike Limited Edition (Oregon) Hat Box lets you show your pride for the Oregon Ducks with six unique hats and a commemorative pull-out drawer hat box. Five of the hats—which players will wear on the sidelines throughout the current season—showcase different Oregon helmet designs. The sixth hat is a limited-edition 2012 Rose Bowl Celebration hat, commemorating the team's title and featuring a one-of-a-kind red rose satin lining. The door of the hat box displays the school fight song, and each of the drawers showcase the Oregon Ducks' signature black chrome wing design and chrome logos.
